OL,6,FRealey was charged with two counts of
OL,7,Fstalking involving serious alarm or
OL,8,Fdistress, and one count of sending an
OL,9,Foffensive, indecent, obscene or
OL,10,Fmenacing message.
OL,12,FShe admitted all of the offences and
OL,13,Fwas sentenced at Isle of Wight Crown
OL,14,FCourt to 18 months in prison.
OL,16,FPC Caroline Woodgate said: "Realey's
OL,17,Fbehaviour has been nothing short of
OL,18,Fhorrendous, and the relentless abuse
OL,19,Fthat local residents have suffered has
OL,20,Fbeen appalling.
